{"tid":1823,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日同好耐無見嘅朋友行街","createTime":"2016-11-25T17:10:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-26T05:13:26.000Z","uid":9586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1ac62e1f3414bf126151a6585f6310a755a99da3","tid":1823,"uid":9586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T17:10:45.000Z","msg":"今日約咗佢係銅鑼灣等 ，三點鐘係時代見到個著住短袖T恤加短褲同件普通白色長外套加個藍色背囊嘅人行岀嚟，幾靚喎，當場望多幾眼啦，佢又望住我之後仲行過嚟<br />\n「喂！好耐無見啦！」<br />\n我呆咗呆嘅同時又聞到佢噴左香水，當然大力索多幾下啦<br />\n「係啊，成個唔同哂喎，皮膚又好咗，仲學人扎辮添喎，大把人追啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n佢就笑一笑<br />\n「咪玩啦，邊到有啊」<br />\n咁耐無見，我地本身都好熟，所以就攬咗一陣，我話不如行下囉，佢話等陣，企咗成分鐘之後佢將個背囊向前咩，就開始行街，行行下佢繞住我隻手，太突然令我好難俾到反應佢，仲偷偷錫咗我一啖就話下次不如上嚟我到玩啊！我唔知點答佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人教我應該點答<br />\n<br />\n其實佢係收我做兵定係真係想同我發展？"},{"pid":"b5236776280a8d69c70e7542aebecb1c57e725f6","tid":1823,"uid":9586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T17:17:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"533605fcdd2ecc9f057dc5caecb8a7061fe75466","tid":1823,"uid":9586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T17:18:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d269303820ebb09dd492d02c85462b69f6066fd","tid":1823,"uid":9586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T17:19:14.000Z","msg":"毒撚無人覆"},{"pid":"c60d7af74bda9e2b4d6f35059508b6cee7faca1f","tid":1823,"uid":2949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T17:19:21.000Z","msg":"望下佢有冇扯咪知"},{"pid":"e7424f3bf1159c744129601c339c4faf07a59397","tid":1823,"uid":9586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T17:19:27.000Z","msg":"十連"},{"pid":"3b9f161bc02005df56b27a72732f7e76098cc137","tid":1823,"uid":2515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T17:19:29.000Z","msg":"gay味濃"},{"pid":"703cea574183fd4